CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1946, reads: "Social Committee - The annual picnic sponsored by Omega Psi Phi Fraternity last Sunday at North Park turned out to be a highlight of the local season.  Responsible for the success of the event were, left to right: George Harley, Raymond Page, Frank Lavelle and Frank Clark - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: George Harley, Raymond Page, Frank Lavelle, and Frank Clark standing in front of dark curtain, in Harris Studio
